title: League of legends client is not opening
body:
Hello
I am having a problem opening the league of legends client. The launcher works fine but when I click launch it makes the client launch sound but nothing happens.
Help would be appreciated =)

replies.body: i usually hold left click on the launch button for around 30 seconds but even that isn't working anymore :C
Have you tried waiting **a really long time** to see if the EULA will appear?
